      "role": "user",
      "content": "Wait, what? I'm not sure I follow. I need actual technical advice for the backend. Can you skip the analogies and just give me a list of specific architectural changes or configuration fixes to prevent the deadlock and the connection timeouts? I need to present this to my lead in ten minutes.",
